### Agentic Wallet - Agent Endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:3001/agent

### 1. Welcome & Capabilities

# Get AI capabilities and welcome message
GET http://localhost:3001/agent/capabilities
Content-Type: application/json

###

# Query endpoint (GET version with welcome)
GET http://localhost:3001/agent/query
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 2. Chat Interface

# Main chat interface - Welcome message
POST http://localhost:3001/agent/message
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "hello"
}

