# Direct Wallet Operations (No AI - Fast & Free)

### Get wallet address
GET http://localhost:3001/wallet/address

### Get ETH balance
GET http://localhost:3001/wallet/balance

### Get USDC balance
GET http://localhost:3001/wallet/balance/usdc

### Send transaction
POST http://localhost:3001/wallet/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "to": "0x742d35Cc6634C0532925a3b8D400E4C8F8D0C4E4",
  "value": "0.01",
  "data": "0x"
}

### Transfer ETH
POST http://localhost:3001/wallet/transfer/eth
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "to": "0x742d35Cc6634C0532925a3b8D400E4C8F8D0C4E4",
  "amount": "0.01"
}

### Transfer USDC
POST http://localhost:3001/wallet/transfer/usdc
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "to": "0x742d35Cc6634C0532925a3b8D400E4C8F8D0C4E4",
  "amount": "10.5"
}

### Send batch transactions
POST http://localhost:3001/wallet/send/batch
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactions": [
    {
      "to": "0x742d35Cc6634C0532925a3b8D400E4C8F8D0C4E4",
      "value": "0.01"
    },
    {
      "to": "0x742d35Cc6634C0532925a3b8D400E4C8F8D0C4E4",
      "value": "0.02"
    }
  ]
}

### Send sponsored transaction
POST http://localhost:3001/wallet/send/sponsored
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "to": "0x742d35Cc6634C0532925a3b8D400E4C8F8D0C4E4",
  "value": "0.01",
  "paymasterUrl": "https://paymaster.example.com"
}

